if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('base_platform')
and type = 'U')
drop table base_platform
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: base_platform */
/*==============================================================*/
create table base_platform (
PlatformID int identity,
Name nvarchar(20) not null,
IsDel bit null,
AddTime datetime null,
constraint PK_BASE_PLATFORM primary key (PlatformID)
)
go

if exists (select 1 from sys.extended_properties
where major_id = object_id('base_platform') and minor_id = 0)
